title: Sparkling 2Bd+Office Sunny Granite Balcony Prkng Lndry
posting_body: ['Live in a Beautiful, Spacious, All renovated 2 Bedroom, with an Office space, painted decorator colors, with tons of light, Private Balcony to sit and enjoy coffee, a good book, or a visit with friends, a dishwasher, custom cabinets, all updated and Granite counter tops too!', 'This house is filled with respectful, friendly and hardworking young professionals in their 20’s and 30’s.', 'Located steps to the great restaurants and pubs on Atwells Ave and Broadway.', ' About 10-15 minute walk from downcity offices and grad schools.', 'Current residents are buying a house and looking for wonderful new people to replace them in this Beautiful, Spacious place.', 'Huge modern eat-in-kitchen with Stainless Steel appliances including dishwasher, lots of cabinets & counter space and beautiful granite countertops.', 'Enjoy a great view from your balcony while sipping your morning coffee, steps from all the great eateries and pubs on Atwells and Broadway -  just wait ‘till you see it!', 'Beautiful Sunny Living room with bay windows,', 'Large, clean, bright tiled bathroom,', 'Laundry in your apartment,', 'Gleaming refinished hardwood floors,', 'Thermal insulated windows, including 2 bay windows,', 'Efficient gas heating system,', 'Storage & Free Parking on premises.', 'Clean, bright, sunny 3rd floor with private balcony.', 'Available October 1st, America St. #3F,', 'Rent is $2,095/month and lease has a reward clause for people who pay their rent by noon on the first of the month, you can take $100 off the rent, meaning you pay only $1,955.', 'Nice, clean, quiet, NON-smoking, & responsible people are welcome.', 'Residents in the house are all young professionals.', 'Very mature, quiet grad students may be considered with a guarantor, stipend, or sufficient income.', 'All Apartments are PET FRIENDLY, provided you have a clean, quiet and friendly pet.', 'There is a one time $150 non-refundable pet fee and $15/pet/month pet rent.', 'We cannot consider aggressive breeds or aggressive animals prohibited by homeowners insurance.', 'House is well insulated, all systems are updated, utility costs are not included in rent.', 'Good credit and references, plus one-month security deposit are required in advance.', 'You will be signing a one year lease.', 'Pictures show place empty (it is delivered unfurnished) and also with the last residents furniture, so you can see how big the rooms are.', 'If you have high standards and want a great place, look no further,', 'Please TEXT your name and #3F to', 'show contact info', 'to find out more and see the apartment.', 'Happy house hunting!']

title: In need of a retail space
posting_body: ['Hi!', 'In need of a retail space of our own for our art and other little crafty things we find along the way.', 'We have been in the glass art biz for over 20 years and would like to merge other forms of mixed media in our shop along with sustainably sourced vegan goods.', 'We owned and operated a shop in Oregon called ‘The Master Peace’ for 17 years.', 'Being born and bred Massholes, we felt it was time to come home.', 'And what do you know?', '  Mass can be expensive!', 'So Rhode Island here we come!', ' You can find pics online on our Facebook page.', 'We also have an instagram page @themasterpeaceglass … I will post more pics here soon.', '✌️', 'PS, we are pre approved for a small mortgage!', 'Please please please reach out with any ideas!', 'Our ideal situation would be to have a live/work space.']

keep to myself.', 'I do have my Moderna vaccination card and I have never had covid.', 'Please if anyone would be able to help me then I would greatly appreciate it.', 'Thank you.', "My name is money I'll make", 'from working.', 'If any problems occur and I may not be able to pay rent I will make sure to communicate with you.', '- I get up between 5-7 am and go to bed between 9-10 pm for a room to rent in a household in the Gold Beach, Port Orford, Bandon, or Coos Bay area.', 'Self-employed, semi-retired.', 'No pets.', 'No vices.', 'Very quiet, polite, and respectful.', "I'm hoping to find a perfect shared living situation.", 'Everything has gotten so expensive that it has almost become imperative to have a roommate.', 'I am a 64 year old currently living on the Southern part-time.', "If I move back to Portland I'd get a part-time job to earn an additional income.", "I'm intelligent, educated, long history of leadership roles when working.", 'Have been working in guest services roles over the last couple of years.', 'I previously worked in Property Management and also have excellent rental history.', 'I have lived in the same place at the coast for the last two years, have never been late with a rent payment ($1100/mo) and my current landlord loves me', "and I know she'd give me an excellent reference.", "I'm hoping to find a living situation where the person owns their home or condo and would like a mature, stable, incredibly clean person to share their home.", "Preferably I'd like to have my own bathroom as well, but depending on the situation I could be flexible.", "I don't do drugs of any kind, don't smoke, social drinker, don't have a pet, don't entertain and am very respectful of other peoples space and feelings.", 'LGBTQ friendly.', 'Becoming friends would be great, but not necessary.', 'Please reach out to me if this sounds like a potential fit.', 'Thanks.', 'Hello!', 'I would like 2 bedrooms with at least street parking.', Assistant.', 'I plan to go to school and work part time.', 'My son is almost 7 and going into 1st grade.', 'He’s mellow and everyone loves him.', 'My friend will also be living with us.', 'He doesn’t evicted.', 'Open to 3,6,9,12 month leases.', 'We have a 15 yr old cat that just sleeps and leaves no damage to property.', 'I don’t mind paying larger deposit since credit isn’t good and I don’t have much recent work experience.', '(Medical stuff from 2019-2021).', 'When replying please include pictures and a description of the property or a link where it can be viewed.', 'Where the property is located.', 'When it will be available and what rent/deposit will be.', "Hi, I'm a 28 year-old artist, writer/poet, and musician, who relocated to Portland about a month and a half ago, and I'm still seeking an affordable, stable housing situation.", "I work full-time doing prep-work in a restaurant so regular and reliable rent payments will be no problem for me, my price-range is ideally somewhere around 500-700 a month, so that I can not only keep a roof over my head but save-up some money as well, however: I'm flexible.", "I'm very easygoing, very easy to live with, and pretty quiet overall.", "If I'm not at work, I'm usually sleeping, reading, working on creative projects, watching miscellaneous things on the internet or going on walks, etc.", "I'm looking for somewhere to move-in quickly, for next friday the 12th.", 'Hope to hear from you soon.', 'Feel free to reply via email or text/call me.', 'Thanks :)', "EDIT: I don't have a car, so please try to send me openings that are within reasonable bussing distance to the Lloyd District / Laurelhurst area where I work, I'm not sure a multi-bus hour and a half commute to and from work is a good idea (since I already work early mornings Lol).", 'Thanks.', ':)']

title: 3 bed 1 bath townhouse in Edgewood, RI
posting_body: ['Recently renovated owner’s unit, 3 bedroom, 1 bathroom two-floor townhouse (1650 sq ft) in the desirable neighborhood of Edgewood in Cranston.', 'Located just 3 miles south of Providence and a short walk to Pawtuxet Village.', 'The unit sits on the second and third floor of a corner lot that is just steps away from Roger Williams Park.', 'There are two bedrooms on the first floor of the unit, equal in size.', 'One of these is currently being used as an office/spare TV room.', 'The third bedroom is on the second floor of the unit and is remarkably larger with large closets and built in shelving and drawers.', 'Open concept living, dining, and kitchen space with quartz countertops and new stainless steel appliances.', 'A detached garage with one garage space and one driveway space is included, as well as ample basement area for storage.', 'Private fenced in yard and patio space in addition to a second floor porch that offers beautiful sunsets and seasonal water views of Edgewood Lake.', 'There is also a 4x8 raised garden bed available for use in the side yard.', 'The unit has central air and steam heating with a convenient Nest thermostat.', 'Free washer and dryer in basement.', 'Tenant pays electric and oil.', 'Landlord pays water and sewer.', 'Well trained pets are welcome with meet and greet.', 'Tenant must provide proof of renters insurance and pass credit check and income verification.', '12 month lease.']
